high_descs: Walk to the shelves that are immediately to the left of the safe.
Pick up the watch from the top shelf.
Walk to the safe immediately to your right.
Open the safe and put the watch in it, then close the safe.
anns.task_desc: Place a watch inside a safe.

high_descs: Move across the room to face the white shelf on the right side
Pick up the watch that is sitting on the shelf
Carry the watch and turn right towards the white safe
Place the watch inside of the safe to the right of the gold vase, shut the safe
anns.task_desc: Place a watch inside of the safe

high_descs: Head to the left and face the shelf on the right.
Pick up the watch on the shelf.
Head right and bring the watch to the safe on the ground.
Put the watch in the safe.
anns.task_desc: Put a watch in a safe.
